item.description:
We're going to repeat having breakfast at Bickfords Grille at 669 Highland Ave. in Needham. It's right off of 128. Everyone loved it the last time.

After is miniture golf at McGolf located at 150 Bridge Street , Dedham. Cost is $8.

A RSVP is required on the site. When you RSVP please include if you plan to do both activities or if your just joining us for breakfast. That's the only way we know how to make reservations.

This breakfast replaces the cancelled Panera & cancelled Pizoni"s.
item.name: Breakfast at Bickfords Grille in Needham & Miniture Golf
